You have to do these to restore the server:

1. this package has to be install under home dir. Our home dir is /home/prion
2. have to add result_tmp for storing the results of cases in this package.
3. have to add tmp to install all the blast results for cases in this package.
4. install blast and formatdb. We install them here /home/prion/blast/bin/.
5. modify the blast path and formatdb path in single_blast.pl, make_bac_select_database.pl,make_prophage_virus_db.pl.

